  • Constructor Details

    • SoapMessage

      public SoapMessage(SoapMessage that, String schema, boolean isUpgradeOrSchemaChange)
      This constructor serves several functions. 1. It supports upgrade during marshalling of inbound content from SoapMessage to a more specific type. 2. It supports creation of a copy of an inbound messages (from a requstor) to an outbound message (to a destination) using a different schema. 3. It supports initial creation of a response class from a request class for performing work. The last phase after using the constructor for this purpose should be to call relatesTo() to indicate that the newly created message is a reply to the original message.
      Parameters:
      that - The message to copy from.
      schema - The schema to use.
